治療活動運用                            


  	This course contains 1 lecturer and 1 practice credits. Practice is emphasized to facilitate experiential learning about professional issues. It reviews some professional basics and introduces some advanced practice guidelines to prepare the occupational therapy students for fieldwork practice. Through the semester, the crafts, modalities, and techniques are introduced with practice experience. The issues of therapeutic relationship, clinical reasoning, activity analysis and application are addressed to build up the professional identity. Students will learn general skills of activity analysis, adaptation, and application of occupation. The application sessions of this course are designed to introduce the student to various aspects of occupation as they relate to the generic practice of occupational therapy, e.g. activity analysis, application, and adaptation. Acquisition of skills in performing and analyzing activities will be stressed. Activities include needlework, crafts, culinary, carpentry, and occupational functioning.

課程教育目標 

A. 培育具有專業知能的職能治療人才 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

[核心能力]職能治療專業技能
具備職能治療專業技能，以提供個案職能表現之評估、分析與治療的能力。溝通表達及團隊合作之能力
培養適切溝通表達及團隊合作能力，以建立良好的醫病關係及專業團隊互動。獨立思考及問題解決之能力
培養具有獨立思考、臨床推理及問題解決的能力，並能終身學習。 
