課程教材 Course Material
	    1) Crepeau, E. B., Cohn, E.S., & Boyt Schell, B.A. (2008). Willard and spackman’s occupational therapy (11th ed). Philadelphia: Lippincott, Williams & Wilkins.
2) Hersch, G.I., Lamport, N.K., & Coffey, M.S. (2005). Activity analysis: application to occupation (5th ed). Thorofare, N.J., Slack, Inc.
3) Thomas, H. (2012). Occupation-Based Activity Analysis. Thorofare, N.J., Slack, Inc.
4) AOTA (2008). Occupational therapy practice framework: Domain and process (2nd ed). American Journal of Occupational Therapy, 62, 625-683.    

